# Caddy reverse proxy for the sim server (ARCHITECTURE.md section 8).
#
# No domain was purchased for the MVP: sslip.io is a free wildcard DNS service
# where <dashed-ip>.sslip.io resolves to that IP, so Caddy can still obtain a
# real Let's Encrypt certificate (the Vercel HTTPS pages require wss://, which
# needs a valid cert, which needs a hostname rather than a bare IP).
#
# For the current droplet (public IP 67.207.82.96):
67-207-82-96.sslip.io {
	reverse_proxy localhost:4000
}
# When a real domain is bought, replace the block above with:
#   arena.<domain> { reverse_proxy localhost:4000 }
# point an A record at the droplet, and set Vercel's
# NEXT_PUBLIC_SOCKET_URL=wss://arena.<domain>.
